prompt.title: Embedding for Promptbook: Orchestrating Complex LLM Tasks
prompt.content: Promptbook is recommended for complex LLM-based generation tasks, separating code from prompts, orchestrating multiple prompts, and version control of prompts. It may not be suitable for simple single-prompt applications or when streaming is required.
